---
// Organism: ValueProps
// Bento grid showcasing Habitta's key value propositions.
---

<section class="bg-surface-accent px-[clamp(1.5rem,6vw,5rem)] py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1200px]">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2 md:grid-rows-[auto_auto]">

      <!-- Card 1: Flexibilidad Radical (tall left card) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-end rounded-2xl bg-primary p-8 md:row-span-2 md:p-10 lg:p-12 min-h-[320px] md:min-h-[480px]">
        <div class="mb-auto pt-2">
          <svg class="h-10 w-10 text-secondary opacity-80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L15.09 8.26L22 9.27L17 14.14L18.18 21.02L12 17.77L5.82 21.02L7 14.14L2 9.27L8.91 8.26L12 2Z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-white lg:text-3xl">
          Flexibilidad Radical
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/70 lg:text-base lg:max-w-[340px]">
          No somos una constructora tradicional. Somos una plataforma de
          acabados donde tu tienes el control total del espacio que habitas.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Inversion Inteligente (top right) -->
      <div class="flex flex-col justify-between rounded-2xl bg-secondary/30 p-8 min-h-[180px]">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-tertiary lg:text-2xl">
            Inversion Inteligente
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed text-ink-muted lg:text-base max-w-[320px]">
            Proyectos ubicados en zonas de mayor
            valorizacion garantizada.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 flex justify-end">
          <svg class="h-8 w-8 text-tertiary opacity-60" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17" />
            <polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom right: two small cards side by side -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">

        <!-- Card 3: 15+ Proyectos -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 min-h-[180px]">
          <span class="font-display text-4xl font-bold text-tertiary lg:text-5xl">15+</span>
          <span class="mt-2 font-sans text-[10px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-ink-muted lg:text-xs">
            Proyectos en curso
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Construccion Sostenible -->
        <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-quaternary p-6 min-h-[180px]">
          <svg class="mb-2 h-7 w-7 text-white opacity-90" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14" />
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01" />
          </svg>
          <span class="font-display text-sm font-bold text-white lg:text-base">
            Construccion Sostenible
          </span>
        </div>

      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
